(Photo: Southwest Human Development)Final Arizona Gives Day numbers are in.
Started in 2013 by the Alliance of Arizona Nonprofits and Arizona Grantmakers Forum, this is the first time donations surpassed $3.6 million.
Arizona Gives Day is just one of the ways Arizonans are donating to aid nonprofits during the pandemic.
Several other COVID-19 relief funds have been set up to help Arizona nonprofits:The Arizona Community Foundation COVID-19 relief fund.
The Alliance of Arizona Nonprofits COVID-19 relief fund.